title: McKenna
overview: For more than 20 years McKenna Outfitters has been taking guests on outdoor tours through the Central Oregon wilderness. Two years after the accidental death of his brother, Guy, Brick McKenna returns home to make amends and run the family business with his father, Jack, Guy's widow, Leigh, her two children - Rose and Harry, and Brick's sister, Cassidy in what Jack calls - the "Great McKenna Wild"
